com.wedeploy.android

Interface Callback


  • public interface Callback
    This interface should be implemented to be notified when asynchronous requests to WeDeploy finish.
    See Also:
    Call.execute(Callback)

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void onFailure(java.lang.Exception e)
      Called when the request could not be executed due to connection issues or because of an error thrown by WeDeploy
      void onSuccess(Response response)
      Called when the request was successfully executed and with the Response returned from WeDeploy.
